        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="CH2a1468-start">
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T18:16:26.086+09:00">聖人賢者認為人的資質中，沒有比明察事理更好的。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T18:17:39.237+09:00">在明察事理中，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T18:21:51.921+09:00">若果能夠用聰明智慧來辨識人才</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T18:22:05.127+09:00">那麼眾多的人才酒能夠排列楚上下高低的次序，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T18:43:37.247+09:00">所以聖賢(此指孔子)為《易經》作《易傳》的時候，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T18:30:45.858+09:00">文子中就有了君子與小人的不同。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T18:32:20.358+09:00">在編訂《詩經》的時候，就已經根據詩篇的不同意志感情，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T18:34:34.104+09:00">對《風》《雅》《頌》不同風格的詩篇排列了次序。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T18:38:00.871+09:00">在制定禮樂制度的時候</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T18:38:03.628+09:00">就通過禮樂射御書數等方面來考察人的恭敬守常的品德。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T18:55:41.135+09:00">身居帝王指為的時候，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T18:58:15.564+09:00">這些都是拔舉眾多有秀人才，完成地也的事例阿。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T19:00:24.08+09:00">帝業建成後，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T19:00:32.641+09:00">明君和賢臣就一起享受盛名和美譽了。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.46" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T19:06:25.758+09:00">所以唐堯因能夠辨識才能出眾品德高尚的人而著稱，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.47" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T19:06:41.5+09:00">虞舜因人用八愷八元而胠得成效，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T19:06:49.258+09:00">商湯因為提拔任用伊尹而出名，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.49" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T19:43:27.77+09:00">周文王用呂望而被尊崇。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.50" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T19:44:32.283+09:00">根據這些史實可以說，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.51" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T19:45:15.934+09:00">聖人成就化育萬物的德政，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.52" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T19:47:23.526+09:00">有哪個不是運用自己明辨事理的才能尋求發現人才，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.53" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T19:48:45.042+09:00">並且任用他們從而使自己活的安逸呢！</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.58" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T20:48:27.294+09:00">所以孔子不能實現自己的政治理想，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.60" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T21:42:12.404+09:00">但他仍舊用德行，言語，政事，文學四科來給自己的學生生分類，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.61" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T21:32:29.074+09:00">用生而知之，學而知之，和困而學之三等來廣泛地評論天下眾人。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.63" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T21:30:00.32+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.66" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T20:01:26.839+09:00">又讚嘆不偏不倚守常不變的中庸原則來突出聖人的品德。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2a1468_CHANT_001-1a.59" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-09-23T21:37:50.333+09:00">不被各諸侯國提拔任用，</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
